##Ye Qing: 30 days in Wuhan, a pity

Micro-signal Zhenghedao

Features introduced by Zhenghe Island, a high-end social networking platform focused on entrepreneurs.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
During the special period, Wuhan became a city where people all over the country thought about and prayed for blessings. What was the real life of the people of Wuhan after the city closure? With the anti-"epidemic" carried out in an orderly manner, what changes have taken place in Wuhan? What are the remaining issues?

A special "Ye Qing column" has been launched on the island since January 26. Ye Qing, a resident of Wuhan for 40 years, is a scholar and official. In past columns, Ye Qing has documented many observations and experiences in real time, and has been well received by readers for his constructive suggestions.

Ye Qing himself was recently invited to Phoenix Network "One tiger, one talk" program recording, Wuhan Diary was "People's Daily" under the banner of the People's weekly, reprinted. This will be a valuable piece of historical material. Thanks to him, we have a better sense of the progress of the Wuhan epidemic in all its aspects. Wuhan will get better in the end!

Ye Qing, a professor at Zhongnan University of Economics and Law and deputy director of the Hubei Provincial Bureau of Statistics, is next door to blue island

Source: Zhenghe Island (ID: Zhenghedao)

Cruelty and hope are like meat grinders

Writing articles is a kind of enjoyment, however, recently writing articles often choked up, often shed tears.

It's because of the brutal numbers. There are four sets of numbers that must be remembered.

As of 2400 hours on February 22, a total of 64,084 new cases of pneumonia have been reported in Hubei, of which 46,201 were in Wuhan.

A total of 15,299 cases were cured, including 8,171 cases in Wuhan.

There were 2,346 deaths, including 1,856 in Wuhan.

40127 cases were treated in hospital, including 8583 severe cases and 1845 critical cases.

A total of 15,299 cases were cured, including 8,171 cases in Wuhan.

There were 2,346 deaths, including 1,856 in Wuhan.

40127 cases were treated in hospital, including 8583 severe cases and 1845 critical cases.

The grim numbers bring desperation.

Traditional War can hit a sea of tactics, but the war with the virus "to go without a trace" , do not know where the enemy.

This war is the personage skill comprehensive strength manifestation. People are not the only factors to win, the team of experts + can be treated bed + adequate equipment, there will be a chance to win. Even after 30 days, a policy system, medical system and operational system had been set up to deal with the epidemic of NCP, there were still about 100 deaths a day in Wuhan. This virus is so powerful and so cunning.

After 30 days, the nucleic acid test can finally clear zero, bed and other people, Shelter Hospital and other patients, such as discharge from the hospital centralized isolation of people.

After 30 days, the city was quiet. Wuhan has gone from a bustling city to a frozen city. I can't help but think of the 2004 American sci-fi blockbuster the day after tomorrow.

The city's quiet. The hospital's back to normal. Take the fever clinic of Wuhan Seven Hospital as an example.

On January 24th there were more than 1,300 outpatient visits, and since then they have remained roughly between 800 and 1,000.

On February 20th, there were 119 visits, and the number of people coming to see me has changed a lot.

For four hours on the morning of the 21st, only 69 people showed up for inspection.

On January 24th there were more than 1,300 outpatient visits, and since then they have remained roughly between 800 and 1,000.

On February 20th, there were 119 visits, and the number of people coming to see me has changed a lot.

For four hours on the morning of the 21st, only 69 people showed up for inspection.

The city is quiet, the supermarkets are closed, not for individual customers, but for group purchases. It's also rare in the history of world business.

Of course, even if the group purchase, but also have enough vigilance, keep the distance between people, do not crowd, do not rob. In recent days, a joke has become popular among friends in Wuhan: The first group infected before the Spring Festival, the second group infected in hospitals, the third group infected in supermarkets, and the fourth group infected in group buying. Fortunately, I gave the supermarket has made eight suggestions, go to the supermarket to make a suggestion.

The city is quiet, the Internet is quiet. It's the most important thing for people to be stable and united. The early days were filled with horror videos and terrible rumors, and there are still people who are busy inventing and creating them. For example, a bunch of photos of old mobile phones, as a current photo of a funeral home in Wuhan, slander staff, many people have been duped.

Today, the most wonderful refutation is that academician Zhong Nanshan to see Professor Lin Zhengbin how not to wear a mask video, unexpectedly in 2016, "everyone" video.

The city's quiet. The ambulance load is down. It's a direct result.

Gao Dewen, deputy director of the East Lake, an 18-year-old party member, leads a "four-person team of confirmed patients. ".

February 13 was the most difficult day, he said. One day, 27 people were transferred, 21 were seriously ill, were sent to Guanggu three hospitals, Guanggu Tongji Hospital, a hospital in Wuhan, and another 6 were sent to Jiangan Shelter Hospital.

On the 14th, another eight patients were admitted to Hanyang 5 hospital and four to the shelter hospital.

On the 22nd, one person was sent to Wuchang's shelter hospital and three confirmed patients were sent to Liyuan Hospital.

February 13 was the most difficult day, he said. One day, 27 people were transferred, 21 were seriously ill, were sent to Guanggu three hospitals, Guanggu Tongji Hospital, a hospital in Wuhan, and another 6 were sent to Jiangan Shelter Hospital.

On the 14th, another eight patients were admitted to Hanyang 5 hospital and four to the shelter hospital.

"The 'sick' Wuhan is slowly recovering! I look forward to it every day, " he said. The whole country is looking forward to it. Wuhan has become a "frozen city" and the national economy has also suffered "frostbite" .

Zhu Min, Dean of the National Institute of Financial Research at Tsinghua University and former IMF deputy managing director, said on Friday in the Wudaokou Online Lecture Hall:

"It is estimated that the NCP epidemic will affect a RMB1,380 BN reduction in consumption in january-february this year. Of this total, 902.6 billion yuan will be spent on leisure tourism, and 421.1 billion yuan will be spent on catering. But online education spending is expected to rise by 300% and online short video spending by 60% .

A rebound is inevitable, but we need a strong rebound, so we need to work ten times harder."

Indeed, we used to say, "where there is pressure, there is resistance, " like a spring, the smaller the pressure, the higher the spring. Nationally, there will be a huge rebound in consumption in March and the second quarter.

The rate of resuming work nationwide is increasing every day.

As of February 21, among the 23 provinces that have announced the resumption rate, 18 provinces have resumed work rates of more than 50 percent, and coastal areas such as Shandong, Fujian, Jiangsu, Shanghai, Zhejiang and Liaoning have resumed work rates of more than 70 percent, with Shandong leading the list with 79.4 percent.

In 24 cities across the country, the resumption rate has exceeded 80 percent, and all 379 enterprises in Zhoushan and 84 key foreign trade enterprises have resumed work. In Gansu's low-risk counties, where the rate has exceeded 90 percent, emergency response for prevention and control has been lowered to level 3.

The national economic recovery is the greatest support for Wuhan.

Important time point

In Shenzhen 40 years ago, "time is money" and "time is efficiency" .

In Wuhan today, time is life.

"early detection, early isolation, early admission" , we use 30 days, more than 2000 live life to verify.

For 30 days, Wuhan provided the "Wuhan Plan" ——————————————————————————————————————————————————. Namely, Fengcheng, Fengqu, Fengshi supermarket. However, our time has been staggered.

I draw on the People's Daily Collated "Wuhan War "epidemic" 31-day data log" , as "city people" , comb a few important points in time.

On the evening of January 20th, Academician Zhong Nanshan concluded that "people will pass on their knowledge to others. ".

On Jan. 22, Vice Premier Sun Chunlan traveled to Wuhan to promote the work.

On January 23rd, the city was closed.

On January 27, the central guidance team went to Wuhan.

On February 8, Chen Yixin and Wang Hesheng took office in Wuhan.

February 13, the new provincial and municipal party secretaries in place.

February 17th, total lockdown, three days of grid sweeps.

February 19, closed supermarket, only to receive group purchase.

On February 22, the discharged patients were sequestered for 14 days at designated locations (Shelter Hospital, isolation point) .

If the three letters were in sync, what a perfect map for fighting the plague. Unfortunately, history can not be rewritten.

Execution is more important than success

At 4 pm on the 20th, the State Council Information Office held another press conference in Wuhan, introducing that the central guidance team had been stationed in Hubei for 25 days, so that people in Wuhan had a systematic understanding of the "secrets" of the central guidance team.

Local indecision can not be eliminated without the strong supervision of the central guidance team.

On January 27, the third day of the Lunar New Year, a Central Steering Group headed by Vice Premier Sun Chunlan arrived in Wuhan, the "eye of the storm" of the epidemic, with three main responsibilities: First, to supervise Hubei; Second, to guide Hubei in its fight against the epidemic; and third, to supervise.

In fact, when Vice Premier Sun Chunlan arrived in Wuhan on January 22, he made two decisions according to the specific instructions and requirements of the central government, namely, "sealing off the city" and extending the holiday. Without the guidance team, the siege will be delayed, and the consequences will be unimaginable.

We know how the decision to shut down the city came about.

Medical teams have been transferred from all over the country to build Mount Vulcan, Mount Thor Hospital, shelter hospital, more than 400 isolation points..

A lot of scientific decision-making is guided by a steering group.

"four-piece package" for the strongest cadres:

To be brave and innovative, and to win

With the guidance of the Central Guidance Group, the key to the effectiveness of the epidemic depends on the implementation.

Unfortunately, the only thing we lack is execution. The fusion of Instruction and execution will have the effect of fighting the epidemic.

The executive power depends on the cadres who have the executive power. Four came, four of the names can be found from the "loyal innovation" , "never stop winning" . You can take a guess.

When the new cadres arrived for a week or 10 days, various central media issued authoritative reports describing their "week" or "ten days" , and letting the public know the full picture of their busy lives.

Wang Zhonglin: three days after the investigation, and organized three major campaigns, can be called "textbook-style" anti-epidemic model.

First, the use of big data, to find out the trajectory of the diagnosis, to more vigorously carry out epidemiological investigations.

Second, the implementation of the "four laws" :

Isolation point confirmed patients, all sent to the hospital treatment;

Home diagnosis patients, all sent to the hospital treatment;

Non-designated hospital confirmed patients, all sent to designated hospital treatment;

All discharged patients were put under isolation and medical observation.

Isolation point confirmed patients, all sent to the hospital treatment;

Home diagnosis patients, all sent to the hospital treatment;

Non-designated hospital confirmed patients, all sent to designated hospital treatment;

All discharged patients were put under isolation and medical observation.

Third, the 24-hour closure control measures must be strict and strict, with a greater effort to strengthen closed management.

Chen Yixin: He knows Wuhan like the back of his hand.

At an expert seminar in November 2017, he actually said to me, who came to Wuhan in 1979: Ye Qing, you don't know Wuhan better than I do. Every evening when I have no meetings, I spend my evenings on both sides of the Yangtze River and the Han River. I took it later.

On Feb. 8, Chen Yixin appeared in a wechat group of District Party secretaries and district chiefs in Wuhan, referring to a phrase that everyone understands but is hard to do:

The Central Committee of the Communist Party of China (CPC) has decided to "collect all the information it can" , which is a key move to stop the spread of the epidemic and win the war of prevention and control. "It's no use mopping the floor with the TAP on. "

Plain language. His main task is accountability. He stressed that good Battle of Wuhan, grasp the incentive to be serious, grasp accountability, excellent line of fire promotion, unqualified prompt accountability, to promote cadres to take on, as, dedication spirit.

As of February 21, Wuhan has promoted 20 cadres and 34 members of the Party for fire-line development; Discipline Inspection and supervision authorities have investigated and dealt with 385 problems, dealt with 620 people in terms of accountability, 6 cadres at the bureau level and 127 at the department level.

On the afternoon of the 22nd, Chen Yixin convened a meeting with some Wuhan Alumni and representatives of Chu merchants. "after leaving Wuhan for more than two years, I came back wearing a mask and met everyone with mixed feelings. "

Millions of alumni, Wuhan's greatest wealth. Alumni went from intelligence to Han to defend Wuhan. It can be expected that a large-scale, global coverage of Wuhan Alumni, the World Battle of Wuhan will be pulled open.

Ying Yong: to see the deeds of Dr. Li Wenliang, like ordinary people shed tears. Whenever I have time, I read the comments on the Internet. If it wasn't for the press, we wouldn't know the details.

Hubei Provincial Party Secretary Ying Yong chaired a video conference on Epidemic Prevention and control on Thursday, emphasizing the "six essentials, " the most critical and the latest strategy in the first "four should do four. ". It's a responsible attitude.

We must focus on the two key links of treatment and isolation, carry out large-scale screening of Split Second, realize screening "acceleration" , full coverage of admission and treatment, early intervention in treatment, strict management of fever patients, the real realization should be separated, should be collected, should check, should rule.

The latest decision in Wuhan was to lock patients out of hospital for up to 14 days in a concentrated isolation facility.

Wang Hesheng: As the vice director of the National Health Commission, with a complete medical professional knowledge structure, long-term work in the health care system, is now a member of the Standing Committee of Hubei Province, also as the director of the Provincial Health Commission. One of the few in the country.

These four, I inappropriately compared as the strongest "four-piece set" . I sincerely hope that the four of them will be able to work in Hubei for a long time, not only for the victory of this war against the plague.

In short, Hubei Needs China's most powerful provincial and municipal leadership. When the team is strong and the level of innovation is high, Hubei will develop quickly. This is my experience in Hubei Province for 40 years.

Former "innovation King" Zhang Zhidong, one person, 18 years after the creation of "Great Shanghai" , "Great Wuhan" Miracle.

Nearly 441 days after 2017, Chen Yixin created 10 replicable experiences in Wuhan and became an Internet celebrity city.

We will give the people of the whole country a different Hubei.

The backbone of intellectuals is more important than subsidies

Since January 23, I have been "locked up" in Wuhan. I keep a diary every day, and I think about questions all the time. Always remember the ancestors of Hubei, "the road is long and its repair far, I will go up and down and seek" spirit.

Netizens called me "China's most unorthodox official" , which is just right to play a positive role. This is "non-party personage + representative member + network personage" , three in one personage just come in handy.

My mission is: Just Sow, do not ask harvest, people-oriented can be. "Do one's best, do one's best, " is my motto, the bus reform is my masterpiece.

I put my suggestions through four channels: the Provincial People's Congress, the Provincial People's Political Consultative Conference, the Wechat APP, the State Council's APP APP, and the appeal on Weibo.

What I'm most happy about is that the things I care about are taken seriously and become a reality.

For example, I suggest entrepreneurs develop voice-activated, inductive elevators.

On the evening of the 19th, a special express parcel arrived in Yichang from Shanghai after a long journey. Early the next morning, the long-awaited staff will be inside the special equipment installed on the elevator. After some careful debugging, this retrofitted elevator officially opened the "voice control" mode, medical staff only need to report the floor, the elevator can automatically arrive at the destination, so as to maximize their safety.

I called for help to help low-income working class tide over difficulties, even some netizens want to give me money.

My Wuhan Diary will continue to be called "Ye Qing's innovation diary" .

On May 20,2003, after SARS, I went to Hubei Provincial Bureau of Statistics as deputy director. Six months later, in a forum, I argued that Hubei was "at odds with the weather (there was no strategy for the rise of central China at the time) , at odds (far from the economic center, Small and medium-sized investors were reluctant to come) , at odds (the investment environment was not good) " . Soon, provincial leaders will know. I became a "nitpicker" outside the party.

Bus Reform + "nitpicker" , some people say, your career is basically frozen. In this way, I can "single-mindedly make suggestions and devote myself to development" . I came down from the sky. Get Out of the bus book, the subsidy is cancelled. I'M GONNA publish it for free.

The backbone of intellectuals is more important than subsidies.

Think again: Where is the future of Wuhan?

Hubei links the preceding and the following, connecting east to West. Hubei is strong in China.

Only by realizing the rise of the central region can China rise. Judging from the last year or two, the coast as long as "there is a bright sunshine. ". The integration of the bay area urban agglomeration and the Yangtze River Delta has accelerated the development of the coast.

Focus on environmental protection to accelerate the development of central cities in western China. Only the rise of central China is faltering, and only Hubei in central China has "no one to rely on" . Shanxi and Henan are close to Beijing, Tianjin and Hebei, Anhui has smoothly integrated into the Yangtze River Delta, Jiangxi depends on the Yangtze River Delta, Minnan Golden Triangle, Pearl River Delta Development, Hunan to the south.

Without the development of Hubei, the rise of central China will be "a basket of water is empty. ". In a word, Hubei is an extremely important piece to the central region, to the central and western regions, to the economic belt of the Yangtze River, to South China, to Asia and to the world.

Let's take a look at the future of Wuhan and hope that more entrepreneurs will come to invest in Wuhan.

First, Wuhan must build a healthy capital of the world.

You learn from your mistakes. The Lessons of Wuhan will rise to the level of experience. After this painful experience, Wuhan people will not forget the importance of health.

In Zhang Zhidong's Day, Wuhan was a steel city. I once attended a lecture given by Mr. Feng Tianyu, who said that the Hanyang iron mill used to produce 96 percent of the country's steel. In the 1950s, Wuhan was the country's largest steel producer, later surpassed by Anshan. In 1978, "one-meter-seven mill" was put into production, Wisco was the first in the country, and was later surpassed by Baosteel.

In the 1990s, there was a car, Optical Valley name. For Shipbuilding, bridges, high-speed railway design capacity is super, Wuhan has become the design capital of the world.

Thirty days later, Hubei and Wuhan gathered 32,500 excellent medical personnel from all over the country. Professional doctors come to 10% of the country. Wuhan's ability to fight the epidemic is also super. "Wuhan Plan" in the history of world anti-epidemic left a strong one.

Twenty-two The National Committee of the Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference, who do not seem to be from Hubei, have proposed that January 23 of each year be designated as the National Day of the fight against the plague, with a park and museum dedicated to fighting the disease.

I suggest we put the park in the south mouth of Hanyang. According to international practice, a country's longest river, and the largest tributaries, formed the intersection, can be called the name of the country.

So, the southbank mouth is China，TG. . Where the two rivers meet, Wuhan is the geographical "heart" of China. In the spring of 2020, China's "heart" got sick.

Second, Wuhan has also become the core city of public health and safety emergency management.

The recent central meeting proposed to establish and improve the National Public Health Emergency Management System, focusing on the training of personnel, supplies, and traffic. Wuhan is one of the most accessible cities in China.

Third, Wuhan should become a capital of innovation.

Wuhan Has Light Valley, Dunkou and 82 universities, but its ability to innovate is limited. Proposed Yangtze River new city in 2017. I am a member of the Expert Group on the site selection of the new city of the Yangtze River. I strongly suggest that it be placed in the north of Hankou.

And I suggest that the new city of the Yangtze River should be a city of innovation and science. Xi'an has a science and Technology Innovation Port in western China, jointly built by the Ministry of Education and Shaanxi Province. Wuhan should also apply for a science and Technology Innovation Port in the middle of the Yangtze River New town.

This 500 square kilometers, is both the Yangtze River new city, also called the Yangtze River new area. When Henan proposed Zhengdong New Area in 2000, I suggested that Wuhan's "Zhengdong New Area" should be placed in North Hankou.

The National Development and Reform Commission is expected to approve the Wuhan Yangtze as China's 20th New District.

Fourth, Hubei should realize the overall development.

My suggestion is three circles -- Foshan, Wuhan, Xiangyang City Circle, Yangtze River, Hanjiang River, Qingjiang economic belt. The Yichang Metropolitan area is made up of Yichang, Jingzhou, Ensch and Shennongjia, and Xiangyang is made up of Xiangyang, Xiangyang, Xiangyang, Xiangyang and Xiangyang. In this way, the "e triangle" is formed.

Fifth, it is suggested that the three major areas should be tackled together.

Before SARS in 2003, we emphasized economic growth. After 2003 we learned about economic development, the Scientific Outlook on Development. Since 2012, we have attached great importance to environmental protection.

After 2020, we should focus on health care. That is, the supreme leader of the country said that the people's safety and health as an important task of the party governance.

The majority of entrepreneurs should be around these three areas to expand business.

Six industries are about to explode

There's been a lot of writing about it lately. Also hope that you will listen to the heart-to-heart words of those who are in "frozen city" .

First, the health industry, including health care products, health care platform. Huang Qifan estimates that $300 billion will go into public health and safety under the fifteen plan. That's a small number. Disinfection products will sell well, both public and private disinfection products.

Second, non-contact industries. Including voice-activated elevators, sensor faucets. All airports, subways, shopping malls, etc. should be replaced.

Third, online commerce, unmanned hotel. The no touch deal is getting stronger. Thanks to the great power of mobile payments.

Fourth, online learning, business diagnosis, entertainment, video, conferences, offices and other online systems will become more and more mature. Recently, live lectures are very popular. I've been doing it all week, sometimes twice a night.

Five is the industrial Internet, unmanned factory. It's hard to find workers these days, so an unmanned factory would be less of a problem.

Sixth, a step forward in the intelligence industry. Face scanning and temperature measurement should be integrated into one. Health codes are spreading across the country. Just the healthy smart city content, there's a whole bunch of them.

Summary

In 10 days, let's hope the war is over.

In another 10 days, I hope Wuhan can resume work.

Thank you again to the people of the country for your "help in moving" . It's just that the donated dishes are so rare, the Hubei chefs don't know what they are or how to cook them. Try to include a recipe in the future.

Thank you. Thank you, jeongho-shima.
